name: Baby Cheems Inu
description: More than just another MemeCoin; BabyCheemsInu aspires to maintain a positive space for gamers and investors alike! Silently following in the footsteps of it's parent project, BabyCheemsInu grants holders passive native token reflections. BabyCheemsInu offers high quality NFTs and is on the road to be featured in a relatively nice play to earn game.
